Introduction

Lili (유), or Lili Wu, is a Taiwanese singer affiliated with TEN Entertainment. She gained recognition as a contestant on the reality survival show NEXT GIRLZ and is currently a member of the upcoming Taiwanese girl group GENBLUE.
